{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"I'm a contemporary artist and I show in art galleries and museums."},{"time":5000,"text":"I show a number of photographs and films,"},{"time":8000,"text":"but I also make television programs, books and some advertising,"},{"time":12000,"text":"all with the same concept."},{"time":14000,"text":"And it's about our fixation with celebrity and celebrity culture,"},{"time":19000,"text":"and the importance of the image:"},{"time":22000,"text":"celebrity is born of photography."}]},{"cues":[{"time":25000,"text":"I'm going to start with how I started with this concept seven years ago,"},{"time":30000,"text":"when Princess Diana died."},{"time":33000,"text":"There was a sort of a standstill in Britain"},{"time":36000,"text":"the moment of her death,"},{"time":39000,"text":"and people decided to mourn her death in a sort of mass way."},{"time":45000,"text":"I was fascinated by this phenomenon,"},{"time":47000,"text":"so I wondered:"},{"time":49000,"text":"could one erase the image of Diana, actually quite crudely and physically?"},{"time":52000,"text":"So, I got a gun and started to shoot at the image of Diana,"},{"time":56000,"text":"but I couldn't erase this from my memory"},{"time":60000,"text":"and certainly it was not being erased from the public psyche."},{"time":65000,"text":"Momentum was being built."},{"time":67000,"text":"The press wrote about her death in rather, I felt, pornographic ways --"},{"time":71000,"text":"like, \"Which bit of artery left which bit of body?\""},{"time":74000,"text":"and \"How did she die in the back of the car?\" --"},{"time":77000,"text":"and I was intrigued by this sort of mass voyeurism,"},{"time":81000,"text":"so I made these rather gory images."}]},{"cues":[{"time":88000,"text":"I then went on wondering whether I could actually replace her image,"},{"time":93000,"text":"so I got a look-alike of Diana"},{"time":97000,"text":"and posed her in the right positions and angles"},{"time":101000,"text":"and created something that was in, or existed in, the public imagination."},{"time":106000,"text":"So people were wondering: was she going to marry Dodi?"},{"time":109000,"text":"Was she in love with him?"},{"time":111000,"text":"Was she pregnant? Did she want his baby?"},{"time":114000,"text":"Was she pregnant when she died?"},{"time":117000,"text":"So I created this image of Diana, Dodi and their imaginary mixed-race child"},{"time":121000,"text":"and this image came out, which caused a huge public outcry at the time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127000,"text":"I then went on to make more comments on the media and press imagery,"},{"time":132000,"text":"so I started making reference to media imagery --"},{"time":135000,"text":"made it grainy, shot through doorways and so on and so forth --"},{"time":139000,"text":"to titillate the public or the viewer further"},{"time":141000,"text":"in terms of trying to make the viewer more aware of their own voyeurism."},{"time":147000,"text":"So, this is an image of Diana looking at Camilla kissing her husband,"},{"time":151000,"text":"and this was a sequence of images."},{"time":154000,"text":"And this gets shown in art galleries like this, as a sequence."},{"time":158000,"text":"And similarly with the Di-Dodian baby imagery --"},{"time":162000,"text":"this is another art gallery installation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":167000,"text":"I'm particularly interested in how you can't rely on your own perception."},{"time":170000,"text":"This is Jane Smith and Jo Bloggs, for instance,"},{"time":175000,"text":"but you think it's Camilla and the Queen,"},{"time":177000,"text":"and I'm fascinated how what you think is real isn't necessarily real."},{"time":183000,"text":"And the camera can lie,"},{"time":186000,"text":"and it makes it very, very easy"},{"time":190000,"text":"with the mass bombardment of imagery to tell untruths."},{"time":195000,"text":"So, I continued to work on this project of how photography seduces us"},{"time":203000,"text":"and is more interesting to look at than the actual real subject matter."},{"time":210000,"text":"And at the same time, it removes us from the real subject matter,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":215000,"text":"and this acts as a sort of titillating thing."},{"time":220000,"text":"So, the photograph becomes this teaser and incites desire and voyeurism;"},{"time":226000,"text":"what you can't have, you want more."},{"time":230000,"text":"In the photograph, the real subject doesn't exist"},{"time":233000,"text":"so it makes you want that person more."},{"time":237000,"text":"And that is the way, I think, that celebrity magazines work now:"},{"time":240000,"text":"the more pictures you see of these celebrities,"},{"time":244000,"text":"the more you feel you know them,"},{"time":247000,"text":"but you don't know them"},{"time":249000,"text":"and you want to know them further."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252000,"text":"Of course, the Queen goes to her stud often to watch her horses ..."},{"time":256000,"text":"watch her horses. (Laughter)."},{"time":264000,"text":"And then I was sort of making imagery."},{"time":267000,"text":"In England there's an expression: \"you can't imagine the Queen on the loo.\""},{"time":270000,"text":"So I'm trying to penetrate that."},{"time":273000,"text":"Well, here is the image."}]},{"cues":[{"time":276000,"text":"All this imagery was creating a lot of fuss"},{"time":279000,"text":"and I was cited as a disgusting artist. The press were writing about this,"},{"time":285000,"text":"giving full pages about how terrible this was."},{"time":289000,"text":"Which I found very interesting that it was going full cycle:"},{"time":292000,"text":"I was making comments about the press"},{"time":295000,"text":"and about how we know facts and information only by media --"},{"time":299000,"text":"because we don't know the real people;"},{"time":302000,"text":"very few of us know the real people --"},{"time":305000,"text":"but it was going back into the press"},{"time":308000,"text":"and they were publicizing, effectively, my filthy work."},{"time":311000,"text":"So, these are broadsheets, tabloids, debates were being had all about this work,"},{"time":317000,"text":"films were being banned before people had actually had the look at the work,"},{"time":321000,"text":"politicians were getting involved --"},{"time":323000,"text":"all sorts of things -- great headlines."}]},{"cues":[{"time":327000,"text":"Then suddenly, it started to get on front pages."},{"time":331000,"text":"I was being asked and paid to do front covers."},{"time":334000,"text":"Suddenly I was becoming sort of acceptable,"},{"time":336000,"text":"which I found also fascinating."},{"time":339000,"text":"How one moment -- it was disgusting --"},{"time":342000,"text":"journalists would lie to me to get a story or a photograph of me,"},{"time":345000,"text":"saying my work was wonderful,"},{"time":347000,"text":"and the next minute there were terrible headlines about me."},{"time":350000,"text":"But then this changed suddenly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":354000,"text":"I then started to work for magazines and newspapers."},{"time":359000,"text":"This was, for example, an image that went into Tatler."},{"time":361000,"text":"This was another newspaper image."},{"time":365000,"text":"It was an April fool actually, and to this day some people think it's real."},{"time":368000,"text":"I was sitting next to someone at dinner the other day,"},{"time":371000,"text":"and they were saying there's this great image of the Queen"},{"time":373000,"text":"sitting outside William Hill."},{"time":375000,"text":"They thought it was real."}]},{"cues":[{"time":377000,"text":"I was exploring, at the time, the hyperbole of icons --"},{"time":381000,"text":"and Diana and Marilyn -- and the importance of celebrity in our lives."},{"time":385000,"text":"How they wheedle their way into the collective psyche"},{"time":388000,"text":"without us even knowing,"},{"time":391000,"text":"and how that should happen."},{"time":394000,"text":"I explored with actually dressing up as the celebrities myself."},{"time":398000,"text":"There's me as Diana --"},{"time":402000,"text":"I look like the mass murderer Myra Hindley, I think, in this one. (Laughter)."},{"time":405000,"text":"And me as the Queen."},{"time":407000,"text":"I then continued on to make a whole body of work about Marilyn --"},{"time":412000,"text":"the biggest icon of all --"},{"time":414000,"text":"and trying to titillate by shooting through doorways and shutters and so on and so forth,"},{"time":419000,"text":"and only showing certain angles to create a reality that, obviously,"},{"time":422000,"text":"is completely constructed."},{"time":427000,"text":"This is the look-alike, so the crafting elements of this is completely enormous."},{"time":431000,"text":"She looks nothing like Marilyn,"},{"time":434000,"text":"but by the time we've made her up and put wigs and makeup on,"},{"time":437000,"text":"she looks exactly like Marilyn,"},{"time":441000,"text":"to the extent that her husband couldn't recognize her --"},{"time":445000,"text":"or recognize this look-alike -- in these photographs,"},{"time":447000,"text":"which I find quite interesting."},{"time":449000,"text":"So, all this work is getting shown in art galleries."},{"time":452000,"text":"Then I made a book."},{"time":455000,"text":"I was also making a TV series for the BBC at the time."},{"time":459000,"text":"Stills from the TV series went into this book."}]},{"cues":[{"time":463000,"text":"But there was a real legal problem because it looks real,"},{"time":466000,"text":"but how do you get over that?"},{"time":471000,"text":"Because obviously it's making a comment about our culture right now:"},{"time":474000,"text":"that we can't tell what's real."},{"time":477000,"text":"How do we know when we're looking at something whether it's real or not?"},{"time":480000,"text":"So, from my point of view, it's important to publish it,"},{"time":486000,"text":"but at the same time it does cause a confusion --"},{"time":489000,"text":"intentional on my behalf,"},{"time":493000,"text":"but problematic for any outlet that I'm working with."},{"time":497000,"text":"So a big disclaimer is put on everything that I do,"},{"time":501000,"text":"and I made narratives about all the European or Brit celebrities"},{"time":506000,"text":"and comments about our public figures."},{"time":512000,"text":"You know, what does Tony Blair get up to in private with his fashion guru?"},{"time":523000,"text":"And also dealing with the perceptions that are put about"},{"time":527000,"text":"Bin Laden, Saddam Hussein, the links that were put about pre-Iraq war."},{"time":533000,"text":"And what is going to happen to the monarchy?"},{"time":540000,"text":"Because obviously the British public,"},{"time":545000,"text":"I think, would prefer William to Charles on the throne."}]},{"cues":[{"time":550000,"text":"And it's that wish, or that desire, that I suppose I'm dealing with in my work."},{"time":555000,"text":"I'm not really interested in the celebrity themselves."},{"time":557000,"text":"I'm interested in the perception of the celebrity."},{"time":560000,"text":"And with some look-alikes, they are so good"},{"time":564000,"text":"you don't know whether they're real or not."}]},{"cues":[{"time":571000,"text":"I did an advertising campaign for Schweppes, which is Coca-Cola,"},{"time":575000,"text":"and so that was very interesting in terms of the legalities."},{"time":580000,"text":"It's highly commercial."},{"time":584000,"text":"But it was a difficulty for me -- because this is my artwork;"},{"time":586000,"text":"should I do advertising? -- at the time."},{"time":592000,"text":"So I made sure the work was not compromised in any way"},{"time":595000,"text":"and that the integrity of the work remained the same."},{"time":598000,"text":"But the meanings changed in the sense that with the logo on,"},{"time":602000,"text":"you're closing all the lines of interpretation down to selling a product"},{"time":608000,"text":"and that's all you're doing."},{"time":610000,"text":"When you take the logo off, you're opening up the interpretations"},{"time":616000,"text":"and making the work inconclusive,"},{"time":621000,"text":"opposed to conclusive when you are advertising."}]},{"cues":[{"time":625000,"text":"This image is quite interesting, actually,"},{"time":628000,"text":"because I think we made it three years ago."},{"time":630000,"text":"And it's Camilla in her wedding dress, which, again,"},{"time":635000,"text":"nearly got re-used now, recently prior to her wedding."},{"time":641000,"text":"Tony Blair and Cherie. And again, the legalities -- we had to be very careful."},{"time":644000,"text":"It's obviously a very big commercial company, and so this little,"},{"time":649000,"text":"\"Shh -- it's not really them,\""},{"time":653000,"text":"was put on the side of the imagery."},{"time":657000,"text":"And Margaret Thatcher visiting Jeffery Archer in jail."}]},{"cues":[{"time":660000,"text":"I then was asked by Selfridges to do a series of windows for them,"},{"time":664000,"text":"so I built a sauna bath in one of their windows and created little scenes --"},{"time":672000,"text":"live scenes with look-alikes inside the windows,"},{"time":675000,"text":"and the windows were all steamed up."},{"time":677000,"text":"So, it's Tony Blair reading and practicing his speech;"},{"time":680000,"text":"I've got them doing yoga inside there with Carole Caplin;"},{"time":684000,"text":"Sven making out with Ulrika Jonsson, who he was having an affair with at that time."},{"time":687000,"text":"This was a huge success for them"},{"time":690000,"text":"because the imagery got shown in the press the day after"},{"time":694000,"text":"in every single newspaper, broadsheets and tabloids."},{"time":698000,"text":"It was a bit of a road stopper, which was problematic"},{"time":702000,"text":"because the police kept on trying to clear away the crowds,"},{"time":705000,"text":"but huge fun -- it was great for me to do a performance."},{"time":710000,"text":"Also, people were taking photographs of this,"},{"time":714000,"text":"so it was being texted around the world extremely quickly, all this imagery."},{"time":720000,"text":"And the press were interviewing, and I was signing my book. (Laughter)."}]},{"cues":[{"time":729000,"text":"Further imagery. I'm making a new book now with Taschen"},{"time":732000,"text":"that I'm working on really for a sort of global market --"},{"time":736000,"text":"my previous book was only for the U.K. market --"},{"time":739000,"text":"that I suppose it could be called humorous."},{"time":743000,"text":"I suppose I come from a sort of non-humorous background"},{"time":745000,"text":"with serious intent,"},{"time":748000,"text":"and then suddenly my work is funny."},{"time":753000,"text":"And I think it doesn't really matter that my work is considered humorous, in a way;"},{"time":759000,"text":"I think it's a way in for me to deal with the importance of imagery"},{"time":764000,"text":"and how we read all our information through imagery."},{"time":767000,"text":"It's an extremely fast way of getting information."},{"time":772000,"text":"It's extremely difficult if it's constructed correctly,"},{"time":775000,"text":"and there are techniques of constructing iconic imagery."}]},{"cues":[{"time":779000,"text":"This image, for example, is sort of spot-on"},{"time":781000,"text":"because it exactly sums up what Elton may be doing in private,"},{"time":786000,"text":"and also what might be happening with Saddam Hussein, and George Bush"},{"time":793000,"text":"reading the Koran upside-down."},{"time":798000,"text":"For example, George Bush target practice --"},{"time":801000,"text":"shooting at Bin Laden and Michael Moore."},{"time":803000,"text":"And then you change the photograph he's shooting at,"},{"time":806000,"text":"and it suddenly becomes rather grim and maybe less accessible. (Laughter)."},{"time":810000,"text":"Tony Blair being used as a mounting block,"},{"time":815000,"text":"and Rumsfeld and Bush laughing with some Abu Ghraib photos behind,"},{"time":819000,"text":"and the seriousness, or the intellect, of Bush."},{"time":824000,"text":"And also, commenting on the behind the scenes --"},{"time":828000,"text":"well, as we know now -- what goes on in prisons."},{"time":832000,"text":"And in fact, George Bush and Tony Blair"},{"time":835000,"text":"are having great fun during all of this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":839000,"text":"And really commenting, you know,"},{"time":842000,"text":"based on the perception we have of the celebrities."},{"time":845000,"text":"What Jack Nicholson might be up to in his celebrity life,"},{"time":849000,"text":"and the fact that he tried to ... he had a bit of road rage"},{"time":851000,"text":"and golf-clubbed a driver the other day."},{"time":857000,"text":"I mean, it's extremely difficult to find these look-alikes,"},{"time":860000,"text":"so I'm constantly going up to people in the street"},{"time":862000,"text":"and trying to ask people to come"},{"time":870000,"text":"and be in one of my photographs or films."},{"time":873000,"text":"And sometimes asking the real celebrity,"},{"time":875000,"text":"mistaking them for someone who just looks like the real person,"},{"time":878000,"text":"which is highly embarrassing. (Laughter)."}]},{"cues":[{"time":881000,"text":"I've also been working with The Guardian on a topical basis --"},{"time":884000,"text":"a page a week in their newspaper --"},{"time":888000,"text":"which has been very interesting, working topically."},{"time":890000,"text":"So, Jamie Oliver and school dinners;"},{"time":894000,"text":"Bush and Blair having difficulty getting alongside Muslim culture;"},{"time":897000,"text":"the whole of the hunting issue,"},{"time":900000,"text":"and the royal family refusing to stop hunting;"},{"time":904000,"text":"and the tsunami issues; and obviously Harry;"},{"time":909000,"text":"Blair's views on Gordon Brown, which I find very interesting;"},{"time":913000,"text":"Condi and Bush."},{"time":918000,"text":"This image I've decided to show having a reservation about it."},{"time":921000,"text":"I made it a year ago. And just how meanings change,"},{"time":929000,"text":"and there were a terrible thing that has happened,"},{"time":932000,"text":"but the fear is lurking around in our minds prior to that."},{"time":935000,"text":"That's why this image was made one year ago,"},{"time":938000,"text":"and what it means today."},{"time":943000,"text":"So, I'll leave you with these clips to have a look. (Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1038000,"text":"Chris Anderson: Thank you."}]}]}